    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 可爱的熊猫“剪剪“在竹子上愉快玩耍，虫子大军正不知不觉爬上了树，小心避开虫子并用&quot;武器&quot;击败虫子大军！ </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >干净简洁的剪纸画风 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 选择可爱的小动物，对抗种类繁多的虫子大军 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 多种多样的得分方式直通全球排行 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 传承经典和计时模式更加耐玩 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 完全免费，你还犹豫什么！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >亮出你的“武器”！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单操作，适合所有年龄层的玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116760/extras/fa436a834906f1574381310e3a94c26a.poster.avif?t=1729433866\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116760/extras/fa436a834906f1574381310e3a94c26a.webm?t=1729433866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116760/extras/fa436a834906f1574381310e3a94c26a.mp4?t=1729433866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入全球排名！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专注连击，不间断击败虫子可以获取大量分数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116760/extras/1d95db94aa8db7fd832cb3af04f6816c.poster.avif?t=1729433866\" width=620 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116760/extras/1d95db94aa8db7fd832cb3af04f6816c.webm?t=1729433866\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116760/extras/1d95db94aa8db7fd832cb3af04f6816c.mp4?t=1729433866\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >新鲜出炉的商品！</h2><p class=\"bb_para